\tan n
\left|n - (\ell + \frac12)\pi\right|  = \frac{2\ell+1}{2}\left| \frac{2n}{2\ell+1} - \pi \right| > \frac{C_8}{2(2\ell+1)^7}  \sim  \frac{\pi^7C_8}{2^8n^7} 
|\tan x| \sim \frac{1}{|x - (\ell+\frac12)\pi|}\quad\text{ for } x \sim (\ell+\frac12)\pi 
|\tan n| \,\lesssim\,\frac{2^8 n^7}{\pi^7C_8} \quad\implies\quad \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\tan n}{2^n}\quad\text{ converges absolutely.}
